# Avoid `Boolean(...)` casts

- Do not use `Boolean(value)` or `!!value` to coerce to boolean.
- Prefer explicit predicates, e.g. `typeof value === 'string' && value.trim().length > 0`.
- When checking optional numbers, compare directly (`value > 0`) instead of casting.
